Recommendation

For Beast2, I would design this in order:
	1.	Artifact format
	2.	Identity / trust / encrypted bundle format
	3.	Single-hub post office mode
	4.	Custody receipts and delayed delivery UI
	5.	Locality preload logic
	6.	Two-phone opportunistic sync
	7.	Pure mesh village mode
	8.	Wings accounting
	9.	Emergency / partition mode

That path gets you something real sooner, without trying to solve the hardest mesh problems first.

